author: corcoranwill
content: One of the motivations for adding this channel is to serve as a homebase for people contributing to the new PQ-Interop Breakout Room and devnet effort.  You can learn more about the pq-interop [here](https://github.com/leanEthereum/pm/blob/main/pq-interop/pq-interop-pm.md) and find the calendar invite in the Protocol cal.  Calls are on Wed at 2pm UTC.
